[MSI]
Submission Title	International Mouse Strain Resource - RIKEN BioResource Center
Submission Identifier	GMS-RBRC
Submission Description	The IMSR is a searchable online database of mouse strains and stocks available worldwide, including inbred, mutant, and genetically engineered mice. The goal of the IMSR is to assist the international scientific community in locating and obtaining mouse resources for research. These samples are held by RIKEN BioResource Center
